input: Get the UUIDs of time deposit contracts that have a life cycle status of 'Active' and are linked to a specific account holder identified by UUID '01234567-89ab-cdef-0123-456789abcdef'.

output.sql: SELECT UUID FROM TimeDepositContract WHERE LifeCycleStatusCode = '2' AND AccountHolderPartyIdentifyingElements = '01234567-89ab-cdef-0123-456789abcdef';
